{
  "stem": "8569.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, I remember that the Polish factory, the chocolate factory, Wedel opened branches, and there were queues.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we used to go with Isabela to buy chocolates, and this was a big adventure.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also remember that there were probably kitchens opened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, Isabela took me to a public kitchen when there was a soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were having the soup, which was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those were the little vignettes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the restriction against the Jews was, as I mentioned, you know, the lack of employment, the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were many people resettled from other places, coming into the Jewish section.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning, it was confusion and fright.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But at that time, there was-- they were also starting-- the sequence is a little vague in my mind, but the ghetto started.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people were coming from outside towns into the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were all kinds of rumors, and the negative rumors were dismissed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews in Warsaw felt that if all the Jews are being brought into Warsaw, this is with the intention of saving the Jews, just keeping them in one place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this kind of hopeful thinking persisted until and even after the walls of the ghetto started to be built and the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe it was in 1941.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the teachers who could not teach outside of the ghetto organized themselves in the ghetto, and they created an educational system.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Saying that after the war, those certificates of education would be recognized as bona fide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we used to-- I used to go and attend classes in the regular schools that were taking place in different teachers' apartments.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
